Title: Invited
Description: A bid or expression of interest has been invited from the tenderer(s).

Title: Pending
Description: A bid or expression of interest has been submitted but not yet evaluated.

Title: Valid
Description: The submitted bid or expression of interest met the qualification criteria.

Title: Disqualified
Description: The submitted bid or expression of interest did not meet the qualification criteria.

Title: Withdrawn
Description: The submitted bid or expression of interest was withdrawn by the tenderer(s).
